<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Logo - Jefri Design</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            color: #222;
        }
        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #000;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .back-btn:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .project-img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .meta {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        h3 {
            font-size: 22px;
            margin-top: 35px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.7;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #444;
        }
        .color-box {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="index.html" class="back-btn">← Kembali ke Portfolio</a>
    
    <img src="/static/logo.png" alt="Logo kopi" class="project-img">
    
    <h1>Logo</h1>
    <p class="meta">Client: kopi | 2024 | Logo & Brand Identity</p>
    
    <h3>Brief</h3>
    <p>Client butuh logo lokal yang targetnya anak muda. Mau kesan fun, berani, dan gampang diingat pas lewat di Instagram.</p>
    
    <h3>Konsep</h3>
    <p>Gua gabungin ikon dengan tipografi bold. Fontnya sengaja dipilih yang tebal biar keliatan kuat dan nendang. Warna merah kecoklatan biar ngingetin ke fast drink tapi tetep punya karakter sendiri.</p>
    
    <h3>Palet Warna</h3>
    <p>
        <span class="color-box" style="background: #FF3D00;"></span> #FF3D00 - Merah  
        <br><br>
        <span class="color-box" style="background: #FFC107;"></span> #FFC107 - Kuning
    </p>
    
    <h3>Tools</h3>
    <p>Adobe CorelDraw X7</p>
</body>
</html>
